{"tid":1390133,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓警申請通過「正式搜查《PRODUCE X 101》辦公室」！","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:24:09.000Z","uid":74065,"like":28,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"065e6cb3d4e1e45828cd330e0b7e5dc931d6bcd9","tid":1390133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"南韓Mnet節目《PRODUCE X 101》節目播畢後因為投票數有可疑之處，遭到粉絲正式報警求真相，31日媒體公司CJ E&amp;M（電視台Mnet是旗下子公司）遭到警方下了搜查令，而在最後一集直播中負責接受簡訊投票的公司也出面說話了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4248/4248277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4248%2F4248277.jpg&h=28e832e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓網友計算《PRODUCE X 101》票數差竟出現「詭異巧合」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）4248277<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《聯合新聞》報導，針對電視台Mnet《PRODUCE X 101》直播造假爭議進行調查，申請了搜查令後31日正式開始動作，首爾警察廳網路調查大隊將派人到CJ E&amp;M內部《PRODUCE X 101》製作單位辦公室搜查相關資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4273/4273471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4273%2F4273471.jpg&h=be676eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲位於CJ E&amp;M的《PRODUCE X 101》製作單位辦公室遭到搜查。（圖／翻攝自NAVER MAP）<br />\n<br />\n而據韓媒《DISPATCH》報導，負責直播節目現場投票事項的相關機構「mediatoday」受訪表示：「所有資料的原始檔案都還在，我們不可能造假的，我們沒有立場針對（爭議）說些什麼或出面，我們只是把投票資料傳達給對方而已，線上投票等作業都是Mnet負責的。」<br />\n<br />\nmediatoday聲明表示不清楚Mnet是用什麼樣的方式統計票數，僅表達「原始資料都還在」，只是因為有簽約的關係，在Mnet方沒有要求的情況下沒辦法逕自公開。另外，粉絲現在擔心的是最後結果脫穎而出的「X1（엑스원）」11名成員（金曜漢、金宇碩、韓勝宇、宋亨俊、曹承衍、孫東杓、李翰潔、南道賢、車俊昊、姜敏熙、李垠尚）出道會受到影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4273/4273470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4273%2F4273470.jpg&h=72cd6e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲X1日前進行了第一次團體直播。（圖／翻攝自X1推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時拉埋牙降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0f5c83727e7af3947cb0aedfe8fd577eacbf74","tid":1390133,"uid":91238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"製作人做個節目都可能坐十碌八碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675da33dd5e16e52136ea30139380e55fc8b3e72","tid":1390133,"uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"買位出道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e610e48967a92b8467b958d270df920e3dab84b6","tid":1390133,"uid":143093,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3f0f5c83727e7af3947cb0aedfe8fd577eacbf74","tid":1390133,"uid":91238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"製作人做個節目都可能坐十碌八碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"無金敏圭無宋有彬 抵佢坐"},{"pid":"bbf45b544641163c54d32dc0c9c760f11babc6db","tid":1390133,"uid":91238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e610e48967a92b8467b958d270df920e3dab84b6","tid":1390133,"uid":143093,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3f0f5c83727e7af3947cb0aedfe8fd577eacbf74","tid":1390133,"uid":91238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"製作人做個節目都可能坐十碌八碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"無金敏圭無宋有彬 抵佢坐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次我哋大和解，同一陣線支持圭圭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6818b135e662ba9573b10f8a8454309ddb910fa0","tid":1390133,"uid":105605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e610e48967a92b8467b958d270df920e3dab84b6","tid":1390133,"uid":143093,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3f0f5c83727e7af3947cb0aedfe8fd577eacbf74","tid":1390133,"uid":91238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"製作人做個節目都可能坐十碌八碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo